WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:02.911
JACKSON: Those are bite marks.

00:03.040 --> 00:05.509
Flesh torn out with teeth.

00:06.920 --> 00:08.240
(SCREAMS)

00:08.360 --> 00:09.555
This was Bennet Drake's seat?

00:09.680 --> 00:11.000
It was.

00:12.920 --> 00:17.835
As I understand it, the doctors
have passed you fit, Inspector.

00:17.960 --> 00:19.871
There is a savaged man found.

00:20.000 --> 00:21.070
Gustus, I have not...

00:21.200 --> 00:22.554
You have been good, have you not?

00:22.680 --> 00:24.273
I have.

00:24.400 --> 00:26.676
REID: Two small boys
alone and orphaned.

00:26.800 --> 00:31.431
The woman's name, Guluba,
was the word he used for Dove.

00:31.560 --> 00:33.756
What does Mr Dove's brother do?

00:33.880 --> 00:35.791
Reid believed him
to have been the killer.

00:40.200 --> 00:42.396
DOVE: I could never hurt you, Nathaniel.

00:45.120 --> 00:46.758
You will live quiet, easy...

00:47.840 --> 00:50.593
...until all that may harm us
will be put to rest.

00:50.720 --> 00:53.360
Thank you, Gustus.

